# GitHub Models REST API — confirmed working with any PAT (March 2026):
#   gpt-4.1        ← default (best free-tier)
#   gpt-5-mini     (GPT-5 mini, free tier)
#   gpt-4o, gpt-4o-mini, gpt-4.1-mini
#
# NOTE: Claude, GPT-5.1+, Gemini models listed at docs.github.com/en/copilot/
#   reference/ai-models/model-comparison are Copilot Chat only (VS Code).
#   They are NOT available via the REST API with a standard PAT.
#
# Example: python main.py --provider github --model gpt-5-mini

# ── Direct API keys (optional) ────────────────────────────────────
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_key_here
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_anthropic_key_here
